#

Pan-Seared Scallops with Lemon-Butter Sauce

20 min
$20
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-Carb

Cuisine:

AmericanMediterranean

Course:

Main CourseSeafood Dish

Tags:

SeafoodQuick MealElegant Dinner

Description

Deliciously tender scallops seared to golden perfection, drizzled with a zesty lemon-butter sauce.

Ingredients

  • sea scallops: 1 pound
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped (for garnish)
